      <h2 class="heading--box-pink">Any questions? Speak to your training provider</h2>
      <div class="inset">
        <p>Your provider will be able to answer any questions you have about your training.</p>
        <p>Providers can answer practical questions about your placement, including:</p>
        <p><ul>
        <li>what a typical training term is like</li>
        <li>how much time is spent in school or on academic learning</li>
        <li>how you'll be assessed with exams and coursework</li></ul>
        </p>
        <p>Feeling prepared is half the challenge, so if you have anything you feel unsure about, speak to your provider.</p>
